## Skill Sync Model

Team skills live in `~/Projects/empact-team/skills/`. Your local `~/.claude/skills/` contains symlinks into that directory. You run `/sync-team` to pull the latest skills from GitHub. An hourly launchd job also pulls in the background.

- Do NOT edit shared skills directly (only Vlad updates them, then pushes to GitHub).
- To suggest a skill update, open a PR against `empact-partners/empact-team`.
- To create your own personal skill, add it to `~/.claude/skills/{name}/SKILL.md` — it stays local unless Vlad explicitly shares it via the `share-skill` skill.

